Well well well...
In some way, the Twilight Horde and the Shyre Empire are similar, like two sides of the same coin.
The way the former uses gravity is, in some way more primal, more natural...
The way they travel is connected to astral magic in some way.
The network of the magical fields gets more and more intricate, and the answer to its origin gets simpler and simpler.
